'''Bernhard Eitel''' (born 31 August 1959) is a German earth scientist and geographer. 

Eitel was born in Baden. Since October 2007, he has been the [[Rector (academia)|Rector]] of [[Heidelberg University]].<ref>[http://www.uni-heidelberg.de/press/news/538e.html Rector Prof. Eitel: “An invaluable opportunity to aim at goals that would otherwise have been unattainable” - University of Heidelberg<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> 
